
::REQUIREMENTS::

Python v2.6 - http://www.python.org
Scrapy Framework - http://www.scrapy.org
For details regarding installation of scrapy, please visit: http://doc.scrapy.org/intro/install.html

::RUNNING THE CRAWLER::
To run the crawler, go to the directory where you have installed the 'alipi-crawler'.
Type 
'$ scrapy crawl a11y.in'. This runs the crawler. 
The crawler will output a a11ypi_dict.json file, in the same directory.
